{"tid":729231,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多年都冇美斯轉會消息","createTime":"2018-07-04T11:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T01:04:09.000Z","uid":43785,"like":34,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"31be0c41098424b28d5f6bc88cb21f509f884bb5","tid":729231,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"其實小花最應該轉下會去証明自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踢下其他聯賽，跳出自己個圈圈，<br />\n唔係成世都有人講佢靠巴塞圍住佢踢，踢其他球會就做唔到球王。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想美斯離開西甲，試下轉去踢英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去下利/曼/阿/熱，<br />\n呢幾隊幫佢地排陣贏個聯賽冠軍番黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9d7db5fac77e238357aa6d8bb8925c1382d311","tid":729231,"uid":55851,"like":51,"dislike":4,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"去英超踢一早斷腳啦，我地英超鐵衛唔係人咁品"},{"pid":"1b287338b6b3a826fd0039b405240224298ddff4","tid":729231,"uid":34293,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:23:39.000Z","msg":"踢英超不如收山算"},{"pid":"0b3add3ae38f060229bef45b6d56d17b73b480fa","tid":729231,"uid":58811,"like":19,"dislike":7,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"樓主好柒煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> block撚左你"},{"pid":"604136a2c886d397e873544170cbbab86a16b2c9","tid":729231,"uid":43983,"like":52,"dislike":8,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"人地忠心又有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.